    "There was, however, a significant improvement in the outcomes for the critical evaluations when compared to the overall average course marks (paired t test, p = 0.04, mean difference of 9%).",
    "When compared to similar assessment types within the course, there were improvements (mean difference of 7%) within this study for the critical evaluation marks, but decreases for the essay marks (mean difference of 2%) however, neither difference was significant (Table 3).",
